license: MIT
keywords:
  - hydrology
  - water resources
  - Shiny
  - R
  - ANA
  - HidroWebService
  - DuckDB
abstract: >-
  HydroStat Data Explorer is an R/Shiny application for visualization,
  screening, and analysis of hydrological data associated with stations of
  Brazil's National Water and Basic Sanitation Agency (ANA). It combines a
  compact bundled database with session-only user-provided or user-initiated
  hydrological time-series workflows.
